reviewText: Grandson loves it and anything that has to do with the big green machines.
Will probably watch again this winter when snowy and cold outside.  We are true JD farmers and he loves the old stuff.

I bought this DVD for my sons(3 & 4.5 yr), since they love everything associated with tractors.
The DVD certainly lived to the expectations - they watch it quite often.
My husband loves this series and so does my son.  I got this for him for Father's Day and it arrived on time and in excellent condition.  I would use the vedor again in the future.
This video was interesting to my husband, but it didn't hold my 2 1/2 year old's attention. It would be much better for older kids.
